properties.areaDesc: Eastern Tucker; Eastern Preston; Western Tucker; Garrett
properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued January 7 at 12:51AM EST until January 7 at 4:00PM EST by NWS Pittsburgh PA
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow expected. Total snow accumulations of 3 to 5
inches.

* WHERE...In Maryland, Garrett County. In West Virginia, Eastern
Preston, Western Tucker and Eastern Tucker Counties.

* WHEN...From 8 AM this morning to 4 PM EST this afternoon.

* IMPACTS...Plan on slippery road conditions. The hazardous
conditions could impact the morning or evening commute.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...The heaviest snow is expected on the higher
elevations.
properties.instruction:
Slow down and use caution while traveling.

Please report snow or ice by calling 412-262-1988, posting to the
NWS Pittsburgh Facebook page, or using Twitter @NWSPittsburgh

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 8 AM THIS MORNING TO 4 PM EST THIS AFTERNOON
